'''''Have You Seen Drum Recently?''''' yasohotse 1989<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently? | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › films › have-you-seen-drum-re...</ref><ref>HAVE YOU SEEN DRUM RECENTLY - africa.film logo <nowiki>https://africa.film</nowiki> › have-you-seen-drum-recently-a-doc...</ref>, ni film ikaba ikoresha amafoto aturuka muri ''Drum'' archives ikaba ivuga inkuru kinyamakuru n'inyandiko  ku buzima bw'umuco na politiki ya [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]]<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently? | IDFA <nowiki>https://www.idfa.nl</nowiki> › film › have-you-seen-drum-recently</ref> .  Mu myaka ya za 1950, ''Ingoma'' yibanze ku birabura bo mu mijyi baba mu isi yiganjemo ivanguramoko<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently? - MUBI <nowiki>https://mubi.com</nowiki> › films › have-you-seen-drum-recently</ref>. Harimo ingingo zerekeye umujyi wa jazz umujyi w'ubugizi bwa nabi<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently? The Story of a Black ... <nowiki>https://www.films.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>, ibihimbano na siporo byerekanaga ibyiringiro, ibyifuzo no kwiheba byumujyi, umujyi wigishije abirabura<ref>Africa's Media Empire: Drum's Expansion to Nigeria <nowiki>https://www.cambridge.org</nowiki> › history-in-africa › article › a...</ref>.

Iyobowe na Jürgen Schadeberg, iyi filime ikubiyemo amashusho ya Oliver Tambo nk'umunyamategeko<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently? (1989) | BFI <nowiki>https://www2.bfi.org.uk</nowiki> › films-tv-people</ref>, Trevor Huddleston yerekanye ko yamaganye isenywa rya Sophiatown, Nelson Mandela wagaragaye mu bakinnyi bateramakofe, Chief Luthuli wegukanye igihembo cyitiriwe Nobel ndetse n'umuririmbyi Miriam Makeba<ref>Have You Seen Drum Recently ? - Film (1989) - SensCritique <nowiki>https://www.senscritique.com</nowiki> › film</ref> . Umuziki winyuma ushingiye kumuziki wo muri 1950, harimo itsinda rinini, jazz, swing, kwela na [[:en:Tin_whistle|penny whistle]]<ref>Have You Seen 'Drum' Recently? - Where to Watch and Stream - TV ... <nowiki>https://www.tvguide.com</nowiki> › movies › have-you-seen-drum...</ref>.
